<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Solvus | Engineered Real Estate</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@100;200;300;400&family=Space+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/studio-freight/lenis@1.0.29/bundled/lenis.min.js"></script>

<style>
    :root {
        --nav-height: 80px;
        --c-navy: #03060C;
        --c-navy-light: #0A111E;
        --c-white: #F8FAFC;
        --c-cyan: #00E5FF;
        --c-muted: #4A5D7E;
        --font-sans: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
        --font-mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    
    html.lenis { height: auto; }
    .lenis.lenis-smooth { scroll-behavior: auto; }
    .lenis.lenis-smooth [data-lenis-prevent] { overscroll-behavior: contain; }
    .lenis.lenis-stopped { overflow: hidden; }
    .lenis.lenis-scrolling iframe { pointer-events: none; }

    body, html {
        margin: 0; padding: 0;
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        background-color: var(--c-navy);
        color: var(--c-white);
        cursor: none;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .cursor-dot {
        position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 6px; height: 6px;
        background: var(--c-cyan); border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999;
    }
    .cursor-ring {
        position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 40px; height: 40px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.5); border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 9998;
        transition: width 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), height 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), background-color 0.3s;
    }

    #webgl-canvas {
        position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
        z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
    }

    nav {
        position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; height: var(--nav-height);
        display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
        padding: 0 4vw; z-index: 50; mix-blend-mode: difference; color: #fff;
    }
    .brand { font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 3vw; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }

    main { position: relative; z-index: 10; }

    section {
        min-height: 100vh; width: 100vw;
        padding: calc(var(--nav-height) + 4vw) 5vw 8vw 5vw;
        position: relative;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 11rem); font-weight: 100;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em; line-height: 0.85; margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 6.5rem); font-weight: 100;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 0.95; margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    }
    h3 { font-weight: 200; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem); margin: 0 0 1rem 0; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    
    .mono-label {
        font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 2rem; display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 12px; border: 1px solid currentColor; border-radius: 4px;
    }

    p {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.2vw, 1.3rem); line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 650px; margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0; font-weight: 200; opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .btn {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem; border: 1px solid currentColor;
        background: transparent; color: inherit; cursor: none;
        font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase;
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 2px; border-radius: 40px;
        position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .btn::before {
        content: ''; position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
        background: currentColor; transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); z-index: -1;
    }
    .btn:hover::before { transform: translateY(-100%); }
    .btn:hover { color: var(--c-navy) !important; }
    
    .btn-solid { background: currentColor; color: var(--c-navy); }
    .btn-solid::before { background: var(--c-navy); }
    .btn-solid:hover { color: var(--c-white) !important; }
    .btn-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .trust-strip {
        font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: var(--c-cyan); margin-top: 4rem; display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; opacity: 0.7;
    }

    .dark-sec { color: var(--c-white); background-color: transparent; }
    .light-sec { color: var(--c-navy); background-color: var(--c-white); }
    .light-sec .btn:hover { color: var(--c-white) !important; }
    .light-sec .btn-solid { color: var(--c-white); }
    .light-sec .btn-solid:hover { color: var(--c-navy) !important; }

    .split-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8vw; align-items: center; }
    
    /* SYMMETRICAL SECTION 3 (UPDATED) */
    .symmetrical-outcomes {
        width: 100%; max-width: 1000px;
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
        gap: 120px; position: relative; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .outcomes-divider {
        position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; width: 1px; height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3), transparent);
        transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: -1;
    }
    .outcome-card {
        width: 100%; max-width: 800px; background: rgba(2, 6, 13, 0.6);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); padding: 5rem 4rem; border-radius: 4px;
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), border-color 0.6s ease, background 0.6s ease;
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px); position: relative; z-index: 2;
    }
    .outcome-card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.02) translateY(-10px); border-color: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.4); background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.03);
    }
    .outcome-card p { opacity: 0.6; transition: opacity 0.4s ease; margin: 0 auto; }
    .outcome-card:hover p { opacity: 1; }

    .concepts-wrapper { display: flex; gap: 4vw; margin-top: 5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;}
    .concept-card {
        flex: 1; min-width: 350px; height: 500px; background: var(--c-navy-light); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        padding: 3rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
        transform-style: preserve-3d; perspective: 1000px;
    }
    .concept-inner {
        width: 100%; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;
        transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    .concept-card:hover .concept-inner { transform: translateZ(30px); }
    .concept-title { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 100; line-height: 1; margin: 0; }

    .process-timeline { position: relative; margin-top: 6rem; padding-left: 2rem; border-left: 1px solid rgba(2,6,13,0.1); }
    .timeline-progress { position: absolute; left: -1px; top: 0; width: 3px; height: 0%; background: var(--c-cyan); }
    .process-step { margin-bottom: 6rem; position: relative; padding-left: 3rem; }
    .step-dot {
        position: absolute; left: -2rem; top: 1rem; width: 15px; height: 15px;
        background: var(--c-white); border: 2px solid var(--c-cyan); border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%); transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    }
    .process-step:hover .step-dot { transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.5); background: var(--c-cyan); }
    .step-meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--c-cyan); margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .fit-box-wrapper { display: flex; margin-top: 4rem; gap: 2vw; flex-wrap: wrap;}
    .fit-box { flex: 1; min-width: 400px; padding: 4rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid rgba(2,6,13,0.1); }
    .fit-box.dark { background: var(--c-navy); color: var(--c-white); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .fit-item { margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 200; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem;}
    .fit-icon { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 6px; }

    .stagger-text { overflow: hidden; }
    .stagger-text span { display: block; }
    .outline-text { color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--c-muted); }
    
    .bg-giant-text {
        position: absolute; top: 10%; left: -5%; font-size: 25vw; font-weight: 100;
        line-height: 0.8; color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
        pointer-events: none; z-index: -1; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .light-sec .bg-giant-text { -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(2,6,13,0.03); }

    .progress-bar {
        position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--c-cyan);
        width: 0%; z-index: 100; transform-origin: left;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor-dot" id="cursorDot"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>
<div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>

<nav>
    <div class="brand">Solvus</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <span class="hover-target">Work</span>
        <span class="hover-target">Services</span>
        <span class="hover-target">About</span>
    </div>
</nav>

<canvas id="webgl-canvas"></canvas>

<main>
    <section id="s1" class="dark-sec" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; height: 100vh;">
        <div style="max-width: 1200px;">
            <div class="mono-label fade-up" style="color: var(--c-cyan); border-color: var(--c-cyan);">SOLVUS · EST. 2026</div>
            <h1 class="stagger-wrap">
                <span class="stagger-text"><span>Top 1% in</span></span>
                <span class="stagger-text"><span class="outline-text">their market.</span></span>
            </h1>
            <p class="fade-up">Custom-built. Fast. Yours to keep. Built specifically for US real estate agents who are done renting templates.</p>
            <div class="btn-group fade-up">
                <a href="#book" class="btn btn-solid hover-target">Book a 20-minute call ↗</a>
                <a href="#work" class="btn hover-target">See the work</a>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-strip fade-up">
                <span>BUILT FOR NAR COMPLIANCE</span>
                <span>MLS / IDX READY</span>
                <span>FAIR HOUSING COMPLIANT</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="s2" class="light-sec">
        <div class="bg-giant-text para-text">FAILURE</div>
        <div class="split-grid">
            <div style="padding-right: 4vw;">
                <div class="mono-label">01 / The Problem</div>
                <h2>Most realtor websites are built to sell to realtors, not to buyers.</h2>
                <p>Every Wix template, every Fiverr mockup, every "broker-provided" site is designed to look good in a sales pitch to an agent. It uses stock photos of happy couples holding keys. It has a "Featured Listings" grid that no buyer will ever scroll through. It takes six seconds to load.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="float-y" style="background: var(--c-white); padding: 4rem; border: 1px solid rgba(2,6,13,0.1); box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                <p>Your buyers are not doing a tour of realtor websites. They are on their phone, on Zillow, with their partner in the passenger seat, trying to decide whether you are worth a phone call in the next twenty minutes.</p>
                <h3 style="margin-top: 3rem; font-weight: 300;">That is a different product.<br>That is what we build.</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="s3" class="dark-sec" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
        <div class="mono-label">02 / What You Get</div>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 6rem;">Four outcomes.<br><span class="outline-text">Every site. Every market.</span></h2>
        
        <div class="symmetrical-outcomes">
            <div class="outcomes-divider"></div>

            <div class="outcome-card hover-target float-y" data-speed="1.05">
                <div class="mono-label" style="border-color: var(--c-cyan); color: var(--c-cyan);">01 / LOCAL SERP #1</div>
                <h3 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">You show up when someone Googles "realtor in [your city]."</h3>
                <p>Every Solvus site is built for local search from day one. Google Business Profile setup, city and neighborhood pages, schema markup, real reviews. You stop being invisible.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="outcome-card hover-target float-y" data-speed="1.1">
                <div class="mono-label" style="border-color: var(--c-cyan); color: var(--c-cyan);">02 / LOAD TIME 0.6s</div>
                <h3 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Your listings load in under a second. On any phone.</h3>
                <p>Most realtor sites take 4 to 6 seconds to load. Buyers leave at 3. We build with Astro and ship less than 100KB of JavaScript. Your site is faster than Zillow.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="outcome-card hover-target float-y" data-speed="1.15">
                <div class="mono-label" style="border-color: var(--c-cyan); color: var(--c-cyan);">03 / CONTACT RATE +340%</div>
                <h3 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Buyers call you because the site tells them to.</h3>
                <p>Click-to-call on every page. Contact forms that route to your email and CRM. Lead capture that works on mobile, where 75% of your traffic lives.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="outcome-card hover-target float-y" data-speed="1.2">
                <div class="mono-label" style="border-color: var(--c-cyan); color: var(--c-cyan);">04 / TRANSFER DAY ONE</div>
                <h3 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3.5rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">You own it. No subscriptions. No lock-in.</h3>
                <p>On launch day, all files, hosting credentials, and the domain transfer to you. No monthly platform fees. No ransom if you stop paying. It is yours.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="s4" class="dark-sec" style="background-color: var(--c-navy-light);">
        <div class="split-grid" style="align-items: end;">
            <div>
                <div class="mono-label">03 / Concept Work</div>
                <h2>Three sites. Built to show what Solvus delivers.</h2>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Solvus is pre-launch. The sites below are fully designed and coded concepts for fictional realtors, built to demonstrate our standard. Your site will be designed from scratch for your market.</p>
        </div>
        
