                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 3rem; font-weight: 100; font-size: 3rem;">Built for you if...</h3>
                <div class="fit-item">
                    <div class="fit-icon" style="color: var(--c-cyan);">[+]</div>
                    <div>You close <strong>10 or more deals a year</strong> and are serious about your business.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="fit-item">
                    <div class="fit-icon" style="color: var(--c-cyan);">[+]</div>
